| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5597 — Recovery Inhibition (BrainCipher)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4e9c7d68-d523-5964-a9ab-427c244601aa"
